OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading through the evening, with some
OL,7,Fbrief clear spells likely. Low cloud,
OL,8,Fmist and some light rain or drizzle
OL,9,Fthen spreading inland after midnight.
OL,10,FLess cold than recent nights.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy start with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof light rain or drizzle for some,
OL,14,Fthese easing by the afternoon. Cooler
OL,15,Fthan recently, especially in the
OL,16,Feasterly breeze. Turning sunny from
OL,17,Fthe east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
